longBusinessSummary: Worldwide Strategies Inc., a digital health and fitness technology company, provides fitness experiences and solutions through a mobile application. The company was formerly known as Barnett Energy Corporation and changed to Worldwide Strategies Inc., in June 2005. The company was incorporated in 1998 and is based in Pembroke Pines, Florida.
